logic.dataPreservation

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.dataPreservation.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    Logger for the game. Uses the singleton pattern, so that there can only be one single instance of this logger. The constructor is private and the instance can only be retuned be the corresponding static getter method.
